item.dc:creator: @Zirakac Zirakac
item.description:
@Zirakac wrote:

WhatIsMyIP.com®

What Is My IP? Shows your real public IP address - IPv4 - IPv6

IPv4 Address, IPv6 Address, IP Address Lookup, Change IP, Hide IP, IP WHOIS, Internet Speed Test, Trace An Email, Host Name Lookup, User Agent, Server Headers Check, IP Commands


Tells your Ip Address for your Internet… But not your router to find out your router
click on the two flashing computers at the bottom right corner if you don’t see any then click on NetWork
Connections in Control panel and one of them is your router.
usually its 192.168.0.100…
